    "description": "通过收集可联动能力模块,构建强力的角色以抵御成群的独眼巨人. 《Cyclo Chambers》是一款快节奏,自顶至下的竞技射击游戏,并附带有轻度Rouge元素.多达150种能力模块可供选择,奇思妙想的Build为每一局游戏都带来不一样的体验.灵感来自于《Robotron 2084》等.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/4f3cbb981c64f4a158202896bc1a18a8.poster.avif?t=1726138736\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/4f3cbb981c64f4a158202896bc1a18a8.webm?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/4f3cbb981c64f4a158202896bc1a18a8.mp4?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>遥远的未知星系,一只名为”星际战猪”的生物漫游在宇宙之间,强大且深入人心.仅仅是听到他的名字就令人闻风丧胆.然而,好似其他生物那般,这只野兽有一个致命的弱点 – 为了生存,必须以快乐为食物.<br>不幸的是,这种形式的活动在浩瀚无垠的宇宙中是极为稀少的<br>为了满足他的食欲以供生存,星际战猪命令随从们建造了充满不同房间的空间站.随后凭借名为”粘液”的神秘物质的力量,创造出了数百万的独眼巨人.<br>为了完成这项邪恶的计划,他需要的最后一样物品是…<br>快乐.一个为了星级战猪的快乐以及为了生存而战斗的人<br>通过自己的权利,这只肮脏的蠢猪从银河系的各个角落掳来10名参赛者,即便他们都不愿参加这场演出<br>现在他们必须为了自由和生命而战斗.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/d17ebca20a346f749910ee5bb42e4578.poster.avif?t=1726138736\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/d17ebca20a346f749910ee5bb42e4578.webm?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/d17ebca20a346f749910ee5bb42e4578.mp4?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏特色<br></li><li>快节奏,轻度Rouge动作竞技类射击游戏<br></li><li>150余中不同的物品可供选择<br></li><li>4个不同的战斗场景<br></li><li>10名不同的战斗角色<br></li><li>物品各自联动,创造属于你的奇思妙想<br></li><li>自由选择开/关辅助瞄准<br></li><li>快速游戏(20分钟内)<br></li><li>足量的解锁物品与成就</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/2cd126e3a82b7a0447249a1badf09f33.poster.avif?t=1726138736\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/2cd126e3a82b7a0447249a1badf09f33.webm?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146180/extras/2cd126e3a82b7a0447249a1badf09f33.mp4?t=1726138736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
